'''eIF5'''（eukaryotic initiation factor 5，[[真核起始因子|真核起始因子]]5）是一种[[GTP酶激活蛋白|GTP酶激活蛋白]]，可以特异性激活[[eIF2|eIF2]]的[[GTP酶|GTP酶]]活性，而其本身并不具有GTP酶的活性。在[[真核翻译|真核翻译]]起始过程中，当48S前起始复合物结合mRNA，并且使起始Met-[[tRNA|tRNA]]与[[密码子|起始密码子]]AUG正确配对后，eIF5激活eIF2的GTP酶活性，使得eIF2上结合的[[GTP|GTP]]被[[水解|水解]]为[[二磷酸鳥苷|GDP]]；之后GDP结合的eIF2从40S[[核糖体|核糖体]]亚基上解离。由于eIF2以及其他真核起始因子的解离之后60S核糖体亚基才能与40S亚基结合，因此eIF5对于形成具有肽基转移活性的80S核糖体十分关键。

eIF5还参与与其他多个真核起始因子的相互作用。

== 结构 ==
[[File:Eif5_n.png|thumb]]
eIF5含有[[N端|N端]]结构域和[[C端|C端]]结构域两个[[结构域|结构域]]。

其N端结构域为α/β型折叠，含有两个具有[[核苷酸|核苷酸]]结合活性的亚结构域、一个[[锌指|锌指]]结构以及一个在小GTP酶中普遍存在的[[精氨酸指|精氨酸指]]（arginine finger）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Conte MR, Kelly G, Babon J, Sanfelice D, Youell J, Smerdon SJ, Proud CG|title=Structure of the eukaryotic initiation factor (eIF) 5 reveals a fold common to several translation factors|journal=Biochemistry|year=2006|volume=45|pages=4550-8|pmid=16584190}}</ref>并且N端结构域含有完整的GTP酶激活活性。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Das S, Ghosh R, Maitra U|title=Eukaryotic translation initiation factor 5 functions as a GTPase-activating protein|journal=J Biol Chem|year=2001|volume=276|pages=6720-6|pmid=11092890}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Paulin FE, Campbell LE, O'Brien K, Loughlin J, Proud CG|title=Eukaryotic translation initiation factor 5 (eIF5) acts as a classical GTPase-activator protein|journal=Curr Biol|year=2001|volume=11|pages=55-9|pmid=11166181}}</ref>eIF5的N端结构域的氨基酸序列非常保守，表明它能够在不同的真核生物中发挥类似的GTP酶激活活性。

[[File:Eif5_c.png|thumb]]
eIF5的C端结构域是由[[α螺旋|α螺旋]]组成的一个非典型的HEAT结构域，<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Wei Z, Xue Y, Xu H, Gong W|title=Crystal structure of the C-terminal domain of S.cerevisiae eIF5|journal=J Mol Biol|year=2006|volume=359|pages=1-9|pmid=16616930}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Bieniossek C, Schütz P, Bumann M, Limacher A, Uson I, Baumann U|title=The crystal structure of the carboxy-terminal domain of human translation initiation factor eIF5|journal=J Mol Biol|year=2006|volume=360|pages=457-65|pmid=16781736}}</ref>其中包含了2个具有两种序列特征（芳香性或酸性[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]残基）的结构花样，被称为“AA盒”。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Asano K, Krishnamoorthy T, Phan L, Pavitt GD, Hinnebusch AG|title=Conserved bipartite motifs in yeast eIF5 and eIF2Bepsilon, GTPase-activating and GDP-GTP exchange factors in translation initiation, mediate binding to their common substrate eIF2|journal=EMBO J|year=1999|volume=18|pages=1673-88|pmid=10075937}}</ref>对[[酵母|酵母]]的研究发现，该结构域可以与eIF2的β亚基（通过AA盒）、[[eIF1|eIF1]]和[[eIF3|eIF3]]的c亚基相互作用以促进这些真核起始因子组装成在真核翻译起始中发挥关键作用的多因子复合物。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Yamamoto Y, Singh CR, Marintchev A, Hall NS, Hannig EM, Wagner G, Asano K|title=The eukaryotic initiation factor (eIF) 5 HEAT domain mediates multifactor assembly and scanning with distinct interfaces to eIF1, eIF2, eIF3, and eIF4G|journal=Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A|year=2005|volume=102|pages=16164-9|pmid=16254050}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Singh CR, Curtis C, Yamamoto Y, Hall NS, Kruse DS, He H, Hannig EM, Asano K|title=Eukaryotic translation initiation factor 5 is critical for integrity of the scanning preinitiation complex and accurate control of GCN4 translation|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-and-cellular-biology_2005-07_25_13/page/5480|journal=Mol Cell Biol|year=2005|volume=25|pages=5480-91|pmid=15964804}}</ref>此外，该结构域还可以结合[[eIF4G|eIF4G]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=He H, von der Haar T, Singh CR, Ii M, Li B, Hinnebusch AG, McCarthy JE, Asano K|title=The yeast eukaryotic initiation factor 4G (eIF4G) HEAT domain interacts with eIF1 and eIF5 and is involved in stringent AUG selection|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-and-cellular-biology_2003-08_23_15/page/5431|journal=Mol Cell Biol|year=2003|volume=23|pages=5431-45|pmid=12861028}}</ref>eIF5的C端结构域的功能可能是通过蛋白－蛋白间相互作用，来参与翻译起始进程的调控。

== 功能机制 ==
eIF5的促eIF2的GTP水解作用是与很多过程相关的。eIF5的C端结构域能够与eIF2的β亚基的C端结构域相互作用，使得位于eIF5N端结构域的精氨酸指结合eIF2的γ亚基从而激活eIF2γ的GTP酶催化活性以使其结合的GTP水解为GDP。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Das S, Maitra U|title=Mutational analysis of mammalian translation initiation factor 5 (eIF5): role of interaction between the beta subunit of eIF2 and eIF5 in eIF5 function in vitro and in vivo|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-and-cellular-biology_2000-06_20_11/page/3942|journal=Mol Cell Biol|year=2000|volume=20|pages=3942-50|pmid=10805737}}</ref>这个水解作用只能发生在40S核糖体亚基上的eIF2所结合的GTP上。并且eIF5还与起始密码子的识别进程相关，一些研究发现只有起始密码子正确配对，eIF5才能发挥其促GTP水解作用。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Unbehaun A, Borukhov SI, Hellen CU, Pestova TV|title=Release of initiation factors from 48S complexes during ribosomal subunit joining and the link between establishment of codon-anticodon base-pairing and hydrolysis of eIF2-bound GTP|journal=Genes Dev|year=2004|volume=18|pages=3078-93|pmid=15601822}}</ref>

eIF5的GTP酶激活蛋白活性受起始密码子的配对所调控，使之能够对AUG起始密码子的发现作出反应，开始激活eIF2。

